query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `adminAuditLog` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `adminUserId` int NOT NULL,
  `action` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `targetUserId` int,
  `details` json,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `adminAuditLog_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  INDEX `idx_auditLog_adminUserId` (`adminUserId`),
  INDEX `idx_auditLog_action` (`action`),
  INDEX `idx_auditLog_createdAt` (`createdAt`),
  CONSTRAINT `adminAuditLog_adminUserId_users_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`adminUserId`) REFERENCES `users`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
